Spanish and Corsican

                            apertium-spa-cos
===============================================================================

This is an Apertium language pair for translating between Spanish and
Corsican. What you can use this language package for:

* Translating between Spanish and Corsican
* Morphological analysis of Spanish and Corsican
* Part-of-speech tagging of Spanish and Corsican

For information on the latter two points, see subheading "For more
information" below

Requirements
===============================================================================

You will need the following software installed:

* lttoolbox (>= 3.3.0)
* apertium (>= 3.3.0)
* vislcg3 (>= 0.9.9.10297)
* apertium-spa
* apertium-cos

If this does not make any sense, we recommend you look at: www.apertium.org

Compiling
===============================================================================

Given the requirements being installed, you should be able to just run:

$ ./configure
$ make
# make install

You can use ./autogen.sh instead of ./configure you're compiling from
SVN. If you installed any prerequisite language packages using a --prefix
to ./configure, make sure to give the same --prefix to ./configure here.

Testing
===============================================================================

If you are in the source directory after running make, the following
commands should work:

$  echo "TODO test sentence 1" | apertium -d . spa-cos
TODO test translated sentence 1

$ echo "TODO test sentence 2" | apertium -d . cos-spa
TODO test translated sentence 2

After installing somewhere in $PATH, you should be able to do e.g.

$  echo "TODO test sentence 1" | apertium spa-cos
TODO test translated sentence 1

Files and data
===============================================================================

* apertium-spa-cos.spa-cos.dix  - Bilingual dictionary
* apertium-spa-cos.spa-cos.t1x  - Chunking rules for translating into Spanish
* apertium-spa-cos.cos-spa.t1x  - Chunking rules for translating into Corsican
* apertium-spa-cos.spa-cos.t2x  - Interchunk rules for translating into Spanish
* apertium-spa-cos.cos-spa.t2x  - Interchunk rules for translating into Corsican
* apertium-spa-cos.spa-cos.t3x  - Postchunk rules for translating into Spanish
* apertium-spa-cos.cos-spa.t3x  - Postchunk rules for translating into Corsican
* apertium-spa-cos.spa-cos.lrx  - Lexical selection rules for translating into Spanish
* apertium-spa-cos.cos-spa.lrx  - Lexical selection rules for translating into Corsican
* modes.xml                     - Translation modes

For more information
